definitions.definition: A piece of land that stands out (usually into water) from the land surrounding .
A coming out of bedrock or of an unconsolidated deposit to the surface of the ground .
The part of a rock formation that appears at the surface of the ground .

main_definition: A piece of land that stands out (usually into water) from the land surrounding .
